IN THE LIBRARYU.S.A. $16.95Canada $21.95 U.K. £9.99REINFORCED BINDING one evening, Sam meets fellow mouse Sarah, a wild-eyed explorer who loves adventure! Sarah would rather scurry to the tops of the tallest library shelves and roam the darkest corners of the building than read about the places she wants to visit. Unlike Sarah, Sam never climbs up high—he’s too afraid! He’d rather research subjects and write about them.When Sam reveals to Sarah the joy and adventure one can have by reading books, she decides to help him in turn. Can Sarah help Sam overcome his fear of heights? Together this duo shows that, with teamwork and determination, anything is possible.
